            <string language="en">An article in PDF format on the development directions of accounting in the past two decades, especially from the perspective of accounting in finance and management.
http://www.edu.fi/teemat/liiketoimintaosaaminen/kty_75v_ollila.pdf	The challenges of international business know-how	An article in PDF format on the challenges of international business know-how.</string>

          </description>

management.http://www.edu.fi/teemat/liiketoimintaosaaminen/kty_75v_ollila.pdf

finanzas y 
management.http://www.edu.fi/teemat/liiketoimintaosaaminen/kty_75v_ollila.pdf
